description: Me So Hungry Mobile Gourmet Food Truck was created by a team of top chefs & "foodies" with insatiable appetites who are committed to bringing quality gourmet food to the masses without the gourmet price. Using only fresh high-quality ingredients, Me So Hungry serves up a fusion of world flavors that pack a monster-sized punch. They're culinary experts in delivering the "sneak attack": bold flavors, fiery sauces, unlikely combinations, and daily "foodie" specials for their dedicated followers. They change our menu seasonally. Like many of the world's finest restaurants, our regularly changing menus ensure that only the highest quality and freshest ingredients are used in their monster dishes. Available for Private Catering Events, Corporate Sales Meetings, Holiday Parties, Birthday Parties, Wedding Receptions, Product Launch Events, Movie and Commercial Shoots, and any other kind of Company Events.
name: Me So Hungry SF
